="pane-content"> 24 September 2012</div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-user-created-content-panel-pane-3" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="view view-user-created-content view-id-user_created_content view-display-id-panel_pane_3 view-dom-id-15c49c89b881cc1bf2524c6caabaf783"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last"><div class="views-field views-field-views-conditional"> <span class="field-content">Presented by <a href="/users/chris-smith">Chris Smith</a>, <a href="/users/dave-ansell">Dave Ansell</a>, <a href="/users/ginny-smith">Ginny Smith</a>, <a href="/users/kat-arney">Kat Arney</a>.&nbsp;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="media-wrapper"><div class="panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-image" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><div id="file-409435" class="file file-image file-image-jpeg"><h2 class="element-invisible"><a href="/files/images/0003ml0000125000e1dxxx1jpg">0003ML0000125000E1_DXXX_1.jpg</a></h2><div class="content"><fieldset class="collapsible group-image field-group-fieldset panel panel-default form-wrapper" id="bootstrap-panel"><div class="panel-body panel-collapse collapse fade in" id="bootstrap-panel-body"> <img typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-responsive" src="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/styles/featured_image/public/media/images/0003ML0000125000E1_DXXX_1.jpg?itok=AqKqyOM_" width="600" height="400" alt="" /></div></fieldset></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="actions-region actions-top"><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-podcast-play-and-download-panel-pane-1" ><div class="pane-content"><div class="view view-podcast-play-and-download view-id-podcast_play_and_download view-display-id-panel_pane_1 view-dom-id-3a28ac5103254981ff19b4edbb54bc8c"><div class="view-content"><div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last"><div class="views-field views-field-field-podcast"><div class="field-content"><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/Naked_Scientists_NewsFlash_12.09.23.mp3" data-title="Contamination from Curiosity and Beating Bad Memories" data-audio="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/Naked_Scientists_NewsFlash_12.09.23.mp3" class="track"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play" aria-hidden="true"></span>Play</a><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/Naked_Scientists_NewsFlash_12.09.23.mp3" download="Naked_Scientists_NewsFlash_12.09.23.mp3" class="ajax-exclude"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-download" aria-hidden="true"></span>Download</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-block pane-addtoany-addtoany-button pane-addtoany" ><h2 class="pane-title"> Share</h2><div class="pane-content"> <span class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_24 a2a_target addtoany_list" id="da2a_1"> <a class="a2a_button_email"></a><a class="a2a_button_facebook"></a><a class="a2a_button_linkedin"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter"></a><a class="a2a_button_google_plus"></a><a class="a2a_button_pinterest"></a> </span>
